_sText:
HighFall_v1 is a Fun Map for Deathmatch Servers or Fun Matches.
This is my first map.
The Water is invisible. Its No BUG!

On the Map are 16 Spawnpoints for Ts and CTs.
Some Weapons lay on the Ground for the first round where everyone has a Pistol if theres a normal Money System.

If you play this map on a Deathmatch Server so be sure that you use
mp_buytime 999
for Unlimited Time to buy.
The Buyzone is under the Spawnplatform.

I hope you have fun with my Map.

Greetz Krai ;)
